00\li5040 RICHARD\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 How interesting. \par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 BOB\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 So you better keep your friggin nose clean. No violence, not even a parking ticket. This trial is important, and I'm not going to let a lowlife ruin it. But if you do, your family will be moving. How's a pig farm in Nebraska sound?\par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 RICHARD\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 I like it here. You won't have a problem. \par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 BOB\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 Good. Charlie, I'm ready now. \par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 ChARLIE\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 Sure, I'll be right there. \par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s3\fi0\ri1440\li2160 Bob gets in the car and slams the door shut.\par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 ChARLIE (cont'd)}{\pard\plain \ql \sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040  }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 \par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 Here, I've got a couple of things for you.\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s3\fi0\ri1440\li2160 Charlie reaches into his pocket and pulls out a computer disk. He tosses it to Richard. \par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 ChARLIE}{\pard\plain \ql \sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040  (cont'd}{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 )\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 Your next book. "Lulu the Seasick Sea Lion."\par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 RICHARD\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 Marvelous. What else you got for me?\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s3\fi0\ri1440\li2160 Charlie hands over a plastic shopping bag bulging with pasta, sauces, salami and cheese. \par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 CHARLIE \par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 Some souvenirs from your old haunts. A little bit of everything Italian. You still miss it, don't you?\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s3\fi0\ri1440\li2160 Richard looks into the bag.\line \par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 RICHARD\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 I sure do. \par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s3\fi0\ri1440\li2160 Charlie switches off the flashlight.\par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 CHARLIE\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 Who ever said that the U.S. Marshall's Office wasn't considerate? I'll see you around, Richard.\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s3\fi0\ri1440\li2160 Richard lifts the bag to his nose, closes his eyes and takes in a deep whiff. He then throws the bag into the river. \par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb480\f64\fs24\sl220\s2\fi0\ri1440\li2160 INT. richard's home office - DAY\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s3\fi0\ri1440\li2160 Richard sits in his office working on his computer. The disk lies on his desk. \par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 CARLA (O.C.)\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s5\fi-140\ri4320\li4320 (calling from downstairs)\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 Richard? I got to take the kids to camp. Want some coffee before I go? \par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 RICHARD\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 That'd be great.. Thanks!\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s3\fi0\ri1440\li2160 A few moments later, Carla enters and hands him a cup of coffee. \par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 CARLA\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 So, what went on last night?\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s3\fi0\ri1440\li2160 Richard takes a sip and puts the cup down. \par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 RICHARD\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 I have to testify again. This time against Mel Flemmi. \par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 CARLA\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 I remember that bastard. I would have liked to put him away myself. What else?\par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 RICHARD\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 What do you mean, what else?\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s3\fi0\ri1440\li2160 She playfully whacks him on the shoulder. \par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 RICHARD}{\pard\plain \ql \sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040  (CONT'D)}{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 \par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 I thought you had to take the kids to camp.\par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 CARLA\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 And you're trying to change the subject. There's always something else with the Feds. Now tell me.\par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 RICHARD\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 I've got to keep my nose clean, as always. They've got to make sure I'm a credible witness. \par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 CARLA\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 Does that mean not getting into fights at little league games?\par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 RICHARD\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 It wasn't a fight, and it won't happen again.\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s3\fi0\ri1440\li2160 Carla leans over, grabs both of his ears and kisses him firmly on the lips. \par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 CARLA\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 Good. Cause this ain't no game, Richard. I like it here, and so do the kids. You better not screw it up. \par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 RICHARD\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 I won't.\par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 CARLA\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 Good. Because if you do, I'll kill you. \par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s3\fi0\ri1440\li2160 Richard kisses her.\par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 RiCHARD\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 I don't doubt it. \par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s3\fi0\ri1440\li2160 Carla winks at him and leaves the room.\par Richard puts the disk into the computer, opens the file and prints it out. Without even glancing at the paper, he staples the pages together and puts into an Express Mail envelope. \par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 RiCHARD (cont'd)}{\pard\plain \ql \sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040  }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 \par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s5\fi-140\ri4320\li4320 (to himself)\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 Man, writers have it easy. \par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb240