 of the other coaches. We sat right next to him and his boy. In fact, I\par accidentally tripped over him when I went out for popcorn.\par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 TED\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 Do you know what time that was?\line \par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 RICHARD\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 Nope.\par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 TeD\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 And what time did you get back into the theater?\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s3\fi0\ri1440\li2160 Richard gives Ted a confused look.\par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 RICHARD\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 I'm sorry, what did you say?\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s3\fi0\ri1440\li2160 Ted leans forward towards Richard.\par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 TeD\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 You said you left to get some popcorn. What I want to know is how long were you gone?\par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 RICHARD\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 Two minutes. Maybe three.\par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 TED\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 Did anybody see you come back into the theater?\par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 RICHARD\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 Yeah, Ron did, I'm sure.\par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 TED\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 And why's that?\par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 Ri