4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 RiCHARD\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 Way to go Leo! Good eye. Wait for your pitch. \par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s3\fi0\ri1440\li2160 The pitcher winds up and throws the ball. Leo swings wildly and misses. \par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 UMPIRE\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 Steeeriiike!\par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 RICHARD\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 Good cut, Leo. Good cut.\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s3\fi0\ri1440\li2160 The KIDS on the bench now join in CHEERING Leo on.\par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 Kids\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 Go Leo! Wait for your pitch! \par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s3\fi0\ri1440\li2160 Richard looks over at the crowd, focusing in on George Winn. His jaw is wired shut, and there is large bruise on his face.\par He then looks over at Carla who is making her way down the bleachers and heading in his direction. She smiles as she sees Ted walking towards her.\par CLOSE UP of Carla slipping on a sweater as Ted approaches. As she pulls on the left sleeve, we see a huge scratch on her muscular forearm.\par Richard glances again at George Winn, silent and miserable, and back at Carla. Carla gives Ted a friendly greeting and then walks over to Richard.\par Richard gives her a kiss on the cheek and whispers softly in her ear.\par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 RICHARD\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs24\sl220\s6\fi0\ri3600\li3600 Looks like you're 12 for 12 in the Family Game...\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s3\fi0\ri1440\li2160 Carla smiles and leans into him.\par }{\pard\plain \ql \caps\sb240\f64\fs24\sl220\s4\fi0\ri1800\li5040 CarlA\par }{\pard\plain \ql \sb0\f64\fs2